rows.label: qst201502_0010
rows.name:
All of you, come on! We haven't
got all day to spend on this.

rows.label: qst201502_0020
rows.name:
Azami seem very excited for
such simple mission.

rows.label: qst201502_0030
rows.name:
Nah, I'm sure she's just glad to
have all her friends on board.

rows.label: qst201502_0040
rows.name: I think so too.

rows.label: qst201502_0050
rows.name:
Everything is more fun when you can
do it with those you care about, right?

rows.label: qst201502_0060
rows.name:
Still, you did the surveillance
from here?

rows.label: qst201502_0070
rows.name:
Yes, that's right. There couldn't be
a better place for it.

rows.label: qst201502_0080
rows.name:
But there's practically nothing around here.
Seems like an odd choice?

rows.label: qst201502_0090
rows.name: Haha... Just watch. I'll survey the area now.

rows.label: qst201502_0100
rows.name: Two men over in this direction, picking flowers.

rows.label: qst201502_0110
rows.name: Working with an almost tireless determination.

rows.label: qst201502_0120
rows.name:
And there's another. Some kind of scientist.
He's holed up in his room.

rows.label: qst201502_0130
rows.name: Azami see that far away?!

rows.label: qst201502_0140
rows.name: That crazy talk!

rows.label: qst201502_0150
rows.name:
Even with telescope lens of Hana,
Tora still not see that far!

rows.label: qst201502_0160
rows.name:
You've been using your powers to track
those three guys this whole time?

rows.label: qst201502_0170
rows.name: Four guys.

rows.label: qst201502_0180
rows.name: Four?

rows.label: qst201502_0190
rows.name:
Yes. Originally, I had my eye on four
suspicious individuals.

rows.label: qst201502_0200
rows.name:
But one of them recently, shall we say, saw reason...
and now there are three.

rows.label: qst201502_0210
rows.name: What exactly is it that they're doing?

rows.label: qst201502_0220
rows.name: It's difficult to tell, just watching from afar.

rows.label: qst201502_0230
rows.name:
All I can say right now is that they're making some substance
from the flowers and then shipping it out of the country.

rows.label: qst201502_0240
rows.name: Hmm... I wonder what they're trying to do...

rows.label: qst201502_0250
rows.name: You can't identify the genus of flower?

rows.label: qst201502_0260
rows.name:
Sorry, I'm afraid I couldn't tell you.
I don't know much about botany.

rows.label: qst201502_0270
rows.name: All right.

rows.label: qst201502_0280
rows.name:
Hey... Why don't we go up and
ask them ourselves?

rows.label: qst201502_0290
rows.name: What, all three of them?

rows.label: qst201502_0300
rows.name: Yes, all three. If we put the squeeze on them...

rows.label: qst201502_0310
rows.name:
I'm sure they'll be happy to tell us
what flowers they're picking and why.

rows.label: qst201502_0320
rows.name: Hmm, not sure about this...

rows.label: qst201502_0330
rows.name:
I've grown so tired of all this watching
and waiting.

rows.label: qst201502_0340
rows.name:
I wanna finally have some fun with my cutie-pie Driver, haha.
Come on, let's go introduce ourselves.
